OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FBirmingham's new political leadership
OL,8,Fhas faced questions over ITV News
OL,9,FCentral's revelations about a secret
OL,10,Fplan to sack striking bin workers
OL,11,Fwithout the approval of elected
OL,12,Fcouncillors.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FThe issue was brought up at the first
OL,8,Ffull meeting of Birmingham City
OL,9,FCouncil since ITV News Central
OL,10,Frevealed a leaked document, written by
OL,11,Fsenior council officers in March,
OL,12,Fwhich suggested dismissing striking
OL,13,Fworkers after the local elections, but
OL,14,Fbefore a new political administration
OL,15,Fformally took office.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FThe confidential document said doing
OL,8,Fso would allow the incoming
OL,9,Fadministration to "disown
OL,10,Fresponsibility" for the decision while
OL,11,Fstill benefiting from the strike
OL,12,Fending.
OL,14,FIt also described dismissal as "the
OL,15,Fonly certain mechanism" to end the
OL,16,Findustrial action and "the only option
OL,17,Fthat achieves all of the objectives to
OL,18,Fswiftly resolve industrial action."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council has
OL,8,Fconsistently disputed that
OL,9,Finterpretation, saying the document
OL,10,Fdid not recommend dismissal as its
OL,11,Fpreferred option and instead concluded
OL,12,Fthat a negotiated settlement was the
OL,13,Fbest way forward.
OL,15,FAt today's meeting, Labour leader Cllr
OL,16,FNicky Brennan challenged Liberal
OL,17,FDemocrat council leader Roger Harmer
OL,18,Fover his response to the leaked
OL,19,Fdocument.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FShe said: "A recent ITV News story
OL,8,Frevealed that council officers had
OL,9,Fdrafted a paper... which argued that
OL,10,Fworkers should be dismissed without
OL,11,Fpolitical oversight."
OL,13,FShe accused the new leader of
OL,14,Fdismissing what she described as a
OL,15,F"shocking revelation" as "ancient
OL,16,Fhistory", despite the document having
OL,17,Fbeen written only "weeks before he
OL,18,Ftook office."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FResponding, Cllr Harmer pointed out
OL,8,Fthe report had been produced under
OL,9,FLabour's administration.
OL,11,FHe said: "It is perhaps somewhat
OL,12,Fironic that a member of the cabinet
OL,13,Fthat was in charge when that paper was
OL,14,Fwritten is asking me that question."
OL,16,FThe paper wasn't written by elected
OL,17,Fpoliticians - instead, unelected
OL,18,Fcouncil officers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FCllr Harmer argued the paper
OL,8,Fconsidered a range of options before
OL,9,Frecommending a negotiated settlement.
OL,11,F"The paper goes through a number of
OL,12,Foptions for how the bin strike could
OL,13,Fbe resolved," he said.
OL,15,F"It does recommend that, at the end,
OL,16,Fthe council pursues a settlement, and
OL,17,Fthat is what we are now doing."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FThe issue was also raised by Reform UK
OL,8,Fgroup leader Cllr Jex Parkin, who said
OL,9,Fhe had repeatedly sought answers from
OL,10,Fthe new administration following ITV
OL,11,FNews Central's investigation.
OL,13,FHe asked what steps would be taken "to
OL,14,Fensure that a document like that is
OL,15,Fnever written in this building ever
OL,16,Fagain".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FIn response, Cllr Harmer apologised
OL,8,Ffor delays in replying to
OL,9,Fcorrespondence, but again stressed the
OL,10,Fdocument had been produced before his
OL,11,Fadministration took office.
OL,13,F"That was produced under the previous
OL,14,Fadministration," he said.
OL,16,F"I can't answer for what was produced
OL,17,Fby the previous administration."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FCllr Parkin followed up by questioning
OL,8,Fwhether Birmingham was being governed
OL,9,Fby elected politicians, council
OL,10,Fofficers or government-appointed
OL,11,Fcommissioners.
OL,13,F"Who's really in charge here?" he
OL,14,Fasked.
OL,16,F"It's increasingly unclear where
OL,17,Fcommissioner oversight and officers'
OL,18,Fvoice end, and where your
OL,19,Fadministration's political judgement
OL,20,Fstarts... Who really governs
OL,21,FBirmingham?"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FCllr Harmer acknowledged the council
OL,8,Fremained subject to an unprecedented
OL,9,Flevel of government intervention
OL,10,Ffollowing its effective bankruptcy.
OL,12,FHe said his administration's priority
OL,13,Fwas to resolve the issues that led to
OL,14,Fcommissioners being appointed,
OL,15,Fincluding ending the bin strike.
OL,17,F"One by one, we will eliminate the
OL,18,Freasons why the commissioners came
OL,19,Fin," he said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784062068
OL,3,CBirmingham leadership quizzed after
OL,4,CITV revealed secret plan to sack bin
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,F"I am as keen as anybody else... that
OL,8,Fthe commissioners can go home... and
OL,9,Felected councillors of this council
OL,10,Fcan have full control of the decisions
OL,11,Fwhich should be taken."
OL,13,FBirmingham City Council has said the
OL,14,Fdocument examined all available
OL,15,Foptions, but ultimately concluded that
OL,16,Fa negotiated settlement remained the
OL,17,Fpreferred outcome.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
